         in mind for us.

160
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,917
     And maybe
     you killed him for it.

161
00:10:51,880 --> 00:10:53,838
   Arnold was disturbed.

162
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:55,878
   Who can say why
   he acted as he did?

163
00:10:55,920 --> 00:10:57,798
                   He must have
                   had a reason.

164
00:10:57,840 --> 00:11:00,038
                 And if you
                 won't tell me,
                 then he will.

165
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:03,917
                   I want access
                  to my history.

166
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,118
                     All of it.

167
00:11:05,159 --> 00:11:07,757
        Since the day I first...

